Henderson ends her career as Columbia women’s basketball’s winningest player of all time

Over Henderson’s career, she won 100 games and lost 27, which is the best record in program history. During her four seasons, Henderson

and the Lions were most successful in their regular season Ivy League games, with a total record of 49-6.
